#' where
#'   - \mjseqn{E_l^*} is the first estimated actuall ET
#'   - \mjseqn{E_l} is actuall ET from land, `land_evatrans_mm`
#'   - \mjseqn{\gamma} is `param_evatrans_lia_gamma`
